<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='791342' id='t-791342'>Here's what we can do for you.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='794710' id='t-794710'>We can give you a sense</span>
