<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='816207' id='t-816207'>Now here's what I do to fill out the ballot.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='819099' id='t-819099'>I listen to what other people are saying and writing.</span>
